data.title: Just a reminder, ladies, gents and everything in-between.

images.description:
I've been hospital today. It was a cist. I'm just letting you know it's not embarrassing because nurses have boobs too, and let's face it, all nurses are lovely. I had the cist removed there, and then no pain. I was worried about the machines because the ones on adverts, etc, look terrible and look like they hurt, but they don't, and the nurses will make sure you are ok. 
Peace and love always Lauren x

Edit, yeahhhhhh this is my most commented on post! I'm glad my post has reached some awareness, and the light comments have all made me smile, like this Imgur family always do. I fall to sleep lurking in this peaceful community. (As in, it helps me go to sleep), so yeah, keep checking ya titties!!!!  (Can I say that?)
